{"tid":2276073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿森一族8年前預言嘅美國大選開票分布圖","createTime":"2020-11-07T15:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T15:55:31.000Z","uid":310867,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc6e886fd53917dc5fb4ea4258d62337388375c","tid":2276073,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NgxrxE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NgxrxE.png&h=1da324a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012 : Barack Obama vs. Mitt Romney <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGwadcM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGwadcM.png&h=37fdaabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n截至今日的美國2020大選開票情況<br />\n<br />\n「阿森一族」畫面中僅有亞利桑那州的得票與現況不同<br />\n<br />\n報導指，這不是《阿森一族》首次「神預言」未來事件，有粉絲甚至認為編劇是靈媒。<span class=\"red\">2000年，《阿森一族》就預言了川普會當上總統，當年川普只是出名的富商與實境節目主持人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201107/STV2GTTWNBGQ3BIVSVNHXN7SRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201107%2FSTV2GTTWNBGQ3BIVSVNHXN7SRY%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft22XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=4964122c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201107%2FSTV2GTTWNBGQ3BIVSVNHXN7SRY%2F&h=b9426ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201107/STV2GTTWNBGQ3BIVSVNHXN7SRY/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44135ad528a5fa6d09ff5e11ffa95ec30405d606","tid":2276073,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 民主左派 = 支共⇩]<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">[⇩ 左膠 = 西方粉紅⇩]</span></strong></span